item.title: 11 for ’11 (AKA Leigh and Casey make a List)
item.description: Instead of resolutions, this year Leigh and I developed our 11 for 11 - a list of the 11 things we want to accomplish in 2011. I thought it was a good idea so I made two more lists, one for the firm and one for myself. Because I like to overkill things.
